--- !u!114 &8753988290116348462
MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 8307100539313834119}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: c966671dae88ba049a1065faaa878ae1, type: 3}
  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::Shopkeeper
  view: {fileID: 7780843123192267855}
  camRotOffset: {x: 42, y: 180, z: 0}
  defaultEntryDialogue: Take a look at my wares.
  defaultPurchaseDialogue: Thank you for your purchase!
  defaultCannotAffordDialogue: You don't have enough gold.
  dialogueByCharacter:
  - characterId: Springtrap
    entryDialogues:
    - "Ahhh\u2026 metal bones and rotting flesh. You\u2019re a strange customer,
      friend\u2026 but gold spends the same."
    - "You\u2019ve already cheated death once, haven\u2019t you? Let\u2019s see if
      my wares help you do it again."
    - "I know what you did.\u2026 But I sell to sinners and saints alike."
    purchaseDialogues:
    - "A fine choice. Let\u2019s see what horrors you commit with that."
    - Excellent choice, metal revenant.
    - "I wonder\u2026 will this help you escape the suit?"
    affordDialogues:
    - "Ah ah ah\u2026 even monsters must pay."
    - Gold first, monster. Murder later.
    - "You look like you\u2019ve killed many\u2026 surely one of them had gold?"
    - "You\u2019ve waited decades in darkness\u2026 surely you can wait a little
      longer."
